         debconf (>= 0.5) | debconf-2.0
Description: SayIP and node control utilities for AllStarLink
 A set of utilities for AllStarLink nodes to:
  - Announce local IP addresses via DTMF commands
  - Announce public IP address via DTMF commands
  - Control node shutdown (halt) via DTMF commands
  - Control node reboot via DTMF commands
 .
 This package includes:
  - sayip-node-utils.rb: Unified Ruby script for all functionality
  - Audio files for IP announcements and system control
  - Example configuration for ASL3 custom/rpt integration

